{"data":[{"name":"88:1","price":"1. (நபியே! அனைவரையும்) சூழ்ந்து கொள்ளக்கூடிய (மறுமையைப் பற்றிய) செய்தி உமக்குக் கிடைத்ததா?","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ ٱلۡغَٰشِيَةِ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5968,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"hal atāka ḥadīthu al-ghāshiyati ","translations":["Has","(there) come to you","(the) news","(of) the Overwhelming","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["hal","atāka","ḥadīthu","al-ghāshiyati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,1200],[3,1200,2050],[4,2050,3925]]}},{"name":"88:2","price":"2. அந்நாளில், சில முகங்கள் இழிவடைந்து இருக்கும்.","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ خَٰشِعَةٌ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5969,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wujūhun yawma-idhin khāshiʿatun ","translations":["Faces","that Day","(will be) humbled","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wujūhun","yawma-idhin","khāshiʿatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,3160],[3,3160,4965]]}},{"name":"88:3","price":"3. அவை (தவறான வழியில்) அமல் செய்து (அதிலேயே) நிலைத்திருந்தவை.","arabic":"عَامِلَةٞ نَّاصِبَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5970,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿāmilatun nāṣibatun ","translations":["Laboring","exhausted","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿāmilatun","nāṣibatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1210],[2,1210,3985]]}},{"name":"88:4","price":"4. கொழுந்துவிட்டு எரியும் நெருப்பிற்கே அவை செல்லும்.","arabic":"تَصۡلَىٰ نَارًا حَامِيَةٗ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5971,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"taṣlā nāran ḥāmiyatan ","translations":["They will burn","(in) a Fire","intensely hot","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["taṣlā","nāran","ḥāmiyatan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,790],[2,790,1630],[3,1630,3355]]}},{"name":"88:5","price":"5. (அவை) கொதிக்கின்ற ஓர் ஊற்றிலிருந்து நீர் புகட்டப்படும். ","arabic":"تُسۡقَىٰ مِنۡ عَيۡنٍ ءَانِيَةٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5972,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"tus'qā min ʿaynin āniyatin ","translations":["They will be given to drink","from","a spring","boiling","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["tus'qā","min","ʿaynin","āniyatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,1090],[3,1090,2070],[4,2070,3715]]}},{"name":"88:6","price":"6. அதில் அவர்களுக்கு(க் கருவேல) முட்களைத் தவிர, வேறொன்றும் உணவாகக் கிடைக்காது.","arabic":"لَّيۡسَ لَهُمۡ طَعَامٌ إِلَّا مِن ضَرِيعٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5973,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"laysa lahum ṭaʿāmun illā min ḍarīʿin ","translations":["Not is","for them","food","except","from","a bitter thorny plant","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["laysa","lahum","ṭaʿāmun","illā","min","ḍarīʿin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1200],[3,1200,2250],[4,2250,3180],[5,3180,4510],[6,4510,7285]]}},{"name":"88:7","price":"7. (அது அவர்களுடைய உடலைக்) கொழுக்கவும் வைக்காது; (அவர்களுடைய) பசியையும் தீர்த்து வைக்காது.","arabic":"لَّا يُسۡمِنُ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِن جُوعٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5974,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"lā yus'minu walā yugh'nī min jūʿin ","translations":["Not","it nourishes","and not","it avails","from","hunger","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","yus'minu","walā","yugh'nī","min","jūʿin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,440],[2,440,1330],[3,1330,1860],[4,1860,2750],[5,2750,3090],[6,3090,6355]]}},{"name":"88:8","price":"8. எனினும், அந்நாளில் வேறு சில முகங்களோ, மிக்க செழிப்பாக இருக்கும்.","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاعِمَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5975,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wujūhun yawma-idhin nāʿimatun ","translations":["Faces","that Day","(will be) joyful","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wujūhun","yawma-idhin","nāʿimatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,2430],[3,2430,5635]]}},{"name":"88:9","price":"9. (இம்மையில்) தாங்கள் செய்த (நல்ல) காரியங்களைப் பற்றித் திருப்தியடையும்.","arabic":"لِّسَعۡيِهَا رَاضِيَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5976,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"lisaʿyihā rāḍiyatun ","translations":["With their effort","satisfied","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["lisaʿyihā","rāḍiyatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1300],[2,1300,2965]]}},{"name":"88:10","price":"10. (அவை) மேலான சொர்க்கத்தில் இருக்கும்.","arabic":"فِي جَنَّةٍ عَالِيَةٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5977,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fī jannatin ʿāliyatin ","translations":["In","a garden","elevated","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["fī","jannatin","ʿāliyatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,2200],[3,2200,3725]]}},{"name":"88:11","price":"11. அதில் வீண் வார்த்தையை அவை செவியுறாது.","arabic":"لَّا تَسۡمَعُ فِيهَا لَٰغِيَةٗ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5978,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"lā tasmaʿu fīhā lāghiyatan ","translations":["Not","they will hear","therein","vain talk","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","tasmaʿu","fīhā","lāghiyatan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,430],[2,430,1330],[3,1330,2280],[4,2280,3975]]}},{"name":"88:12","price":"12. அதில் (இவர்கள் அருந்துவதற்கு) தொடர்ந்து ஓடிக் கொண்டிருக்கின்ற (தெளிவான) ஒரு சுனையுண்டு.","arabic":"فِيهَا عَيۡنٞ جَارِيَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5979,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fīhā ʿaynun jāriyatun ","translations":["Therein","(will be) a spring","flowing","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["fīhā","ʿaynun","jāriyatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,810],[2,810,2400],[3,2400,4174]]}},{"name":"88:13","price":"13. அதில் (இவர்கள் அமருவதற்கு) உயர்ந்த இருக்கைகளுண்டு.","arabic":"فِيهَا سُرُرٞ مَّرۡفُوعَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5980,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fīhā sururun marfūʿatun ","translations":["Therein","(will be) thrones","raised high","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["fīhā","sururun","marfūʿatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,1540],[3,1540,4315]]}},{"name":"88:14","price":"14. (பல வகை இன்பமான பானங்கள் நிறைந்த) கெண்டிகள் (இவர்கள் முன்) வைக்கப்பட்டிருக்கும்.","arabic":"وَأَكۡوَابٞ مَّوۡضُوعَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5981,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-akwābun mawḍūʿatun ","translations":["And cups","put in place","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-akwābun","mawḍūʿatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1340],[2,1340,4005]]}},{"name":"88:15","price":"15. (இவர்கள் சாய்ந்து கொள்வதற்காகத்) திண்டு தலையணைகள் வரிசையாக வைக்கப்பட்டிருக்கும்.","arabic":"وَنَمَارِقُ مَصۡفُوفَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5982,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wanamāriqu maṣfūfatun ","translations":["And cushions","lined up","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["wanamāriqu","maṣfūfatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1350],[2,1350,3005]]}},{"name":"88:16","price":"16. உயர்ந்த விரிப்புகள் இவர்களின் கீழ் விரிக்கப்பட்டிருக்கும். (இத்தகைய சுகபோகத்தில் நல்லடியார்கள் இருப்பார்கள்.)","arabic":"وَزَرَابِيُّ مَبۡثُوثَةٌ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5983,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wazarābiyyu mabthūthatun ","translations":["And carpets","spread out","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["wazarābiyyu","mabthūthatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1530],[2,1530,3475]]}},{"name":"88:17","price":"17. (நபியே! இந்நிராகரிப்பவர்கள் தங்களிடமுள்ள) ஒட்டகத்தையேனும் அவர்கள் கவனிக்க வேண்டாமா? அது எவ்வாறு படைக்கப்பட்டுள்ளது?","arabic":"أَفَلَا يَنظُرُونَ إِلَى ٱلۡإِبِلِ كَيۡفَ خُلِقَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5984,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"afalā yanẓurūna ilā al-ibili kayfa khuliqat ","translations":["Then do not","they look","towards","the camels","how","they are created","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["afalā","yanẓurūna","ilā","al-ibili","kayfa","khuliqat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,2740],[3,2740,3130],[4,3130,4050],[5,4050,4670],[6,4670,5995]]}},{"name":"88:18","price":"18. (அவர்களுக்கு மேல் உள்ள) வானத்தையும் (அவர்கள் கவனிக்க வேண்டாமா?) அது எவ்வாறு உயர்த்தப்பட்டுள்ளது?","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلسَّمَآءِ كَيۡفَ رُفِعَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5985,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ilā al-samāi kayfa rufiʿat ","translations":["And towards","the sky","how","it is raised","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ilā","al-samāi","kayfa","rufiʿat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,570],[2,570,3240],[3,3240,3810],[4,3810,5175]]}},{"name":"88:19","price":"19. (அவர்கள் கண்முன் தோன்றும்) மலைகளையும் அவர்கள் (கவனிக்க வேண்டாமா?) அவை எவ்வாறு நிறுத்தப்பட்டுள்ளன?","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡجِبَالِ كَيۡفَ نُصِبَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5986,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ilā al-jibāli kayfa nuṣibat ","translations":["And towards","the mountains","how","they are fixed","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ilā","al-jibāli","kayfa","nuṣibat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,620],[2,620,1720],[3,1720,2330],[4,2330,3585]]}},{"name":"88:20","price":"20. (அவர்கள் வசிக்கும்) பூமியையும் (அவர்கள் கவனிக்க வேண்டாமா?) அது எவ்வாறு விரிக்கப்பட்டுள்ளது?","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡأَرۡضِ كَيۡفَ سُطِحَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5987,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ilā al-arḍi kayfa suṭiḥat ","translations":["And towards","the earth","how","it is spread out","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ilā","al-arḍi","kayfa","suṭiḥat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1530],[3,1530,2070],[4,2070,3375]]}},{"name":"88:21","price":"21. (ஆகவே, நபியே!) இவற்றை அவர்களுக்கு எடுத்துக் காண்பித்து, இவற்றைப் படைத்தவனின் அருள்களை, அவர்களுக்கு நீர் கூறி) நல்லுபதேசம் செய்வீராக! (இவற்றைக்கொண்டு அவர்கள் நல்லுணர்ச்சி பெறாவிடில் அதற்காக நீர் கவலைப்படாதீர். ஏனென்றால்,) நீர் அவர்களுக்கு நல்லுபதேசம் செய்பவர்தான்,","arabic":"فَذَكِّرۡ إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُذَكِّرٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5988,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fadhakkir innamā anta mudhakkirun ","translations":["So remind","only","you","(are) a reminder","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["fadhakkir","innamā","anta","mudhakkirun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,4020],[3,4020,5240],[4,5240,6615]]}},{"name":"88:22","price":"22. (அவ்வாறே நடக்கும்படி) அவர்களை நீர் நிர்ப்பந்திக்கக்கூடியவர் அல்ல.","arabic":"لَّسۡتَ عَلَيۡهِم بِمُصَيۡطِرٍ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5989,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"lasta ʿalayhim bimuṣayṭirin ","translations":["You are not","over them","a controller","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["lasta","ʿalayhim","bimuṣayṭirin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,660],[2,660,2310],[3,2310,3945]]}},{"name":"88:23","price":"23 எனினும், எவர்கள் புறக்கணித்து நிராகரிக்கிறார்களோ,","arabic":"إِلَّا مَن تَوَلَّىٰ وَكَفَرَ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5990,"juzNumber":30,"foot